<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>心理疗愈 on 📖 爱分享读书</title><link>https://www.ishareread.com/categories/%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E7%96%97%E6%84%88/</link><description>Recent content in 心理疗愈 on 📖 爱分享读书</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.ishareread.com/categories/%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E7%96%97%E6%84%88/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>清明时节，5本关于生死与告别的好书：读懂它们，才算真正活过</title><link>https://www.ishareread.com/p/%E6%B8%85%E6%98%8E%E6%97%B6%E8%8A%825%E6%9C%AC%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E7%94%9F%E6%AD%BB%E4%B8%8E%E5%91%8A%E5%88%AB%E7%9A%84%E5%A5%BD%E4%B9%A6%E8%AF%BB%E6%87%82%E5%AE%83%E4%BB%AC%E6%89%8D%E7%AE%97%E7%9C%9F%E6%AD%A3%E6%B4%BB%E8%BF%87/</link><pubDate>Thu, 02 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.ishareread.com/p/%E6%B8%85%E6%98%8E%E6%97%B6%E8%8A%825%E6%9C%AC%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E7%94%9F%E6%AD%BB%E4%B8%8E%E5%91%8A%E5%88%AB%E7%9A%84%E5%A5%BD%E4%B9%A6%E8%AF%BB%E6%87%82%E5%AE%83%E4%BB%AC%E6%89%8D%E7%AE%97%E7%9C%9F%E6%AD%A3%E6%B4%BB%E8%BF%87/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://www.ishareread.com/" alt="Featured image of post 清明时节，5本关于生死与告别的好书：读懂它们，才算真正活过" /&gt;&lt;p&gt;每年清明，我都会做同一件事——给自己列一份书单。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;不是因为矫情，而是因为这个节日太特殊了。它让我们不得不直面一个平时刻意回避的话题：死亡。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;中国人很忌讳谈死。但越是回避，越是恐惧。反而是那些真正思考过死亡的人，活得更加通透和笃定。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>